<title>ạ̹ydk lmạ tkwn mʿ ạ̹ydy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ạ̹ydk lmạ tkwn mʿ ạ̹ydy .. bttḥqq ậyạt
 wṣwtk lmạ ykwn mʿ ṣwty .. btqwm ạlạ̉mwạt)2
 rwḥk yḥyy ysnd ysẖfy .. wystkẖdmny ạ̉dạh
 ạlqrạr- (mḥtạj lạ̹ydk trfʿny .. mḥtạj lrwḥk ymlạny
 mḥtạj lṣwtk yrsẖdny .. mḥtạjk yạ yswʿ)2
 2- (wḥdk rby mạ fy gẖyrk .. yrạfqny ʿly̱ ṭwl
 ḥkmẗ btʿṭy qwẗ wnʿmẗ .. ạ̉bdaⁿạ mạ btzwl)2
 ạ̉nạ rḥ ạ̉msẖy kẖṭwẗ bkẖṭwẗ .. mʿạk lw llmjhwl</lyrics>
</song>